metadata.description:
I have the pleasure to present to you the "Grey - The Big Cat"

... And there's Fred Life reading a great book at a Hygge moment in "Big" company... 

I challenge you to enter this FredArt and discover all the details.

- What book is Fred Life reading?
- Where is Grey's favorite toy?
- Why did Grey get so big?

Tell me if you found all the details?

Every works is unique, and creates Unique Emotions and Sensations...
 
It's a pleasure to have a 4-legged animal üêæüêæ by our side, I've always loved dogs and I was recently won over by this wild feline and its peculiar personality. Now I say that the important thing is to have these 4-legged friends always around. It is a relationship for life, which provide a good state of mind.
